Package org.hiphap

Class OrganizationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hiphap.OrganizationManager
  • public class OrganizationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class uses the singleton pattern to allow easy access to the Organization data from any point within the system.
